{"tid":1538593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔表示：只剩下一大訴求，寧缺勿濫！！","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:22:34.000Z","uid":190078,"like":26,"dislike":122,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6bb7170521f1530b38e4e8262113afc7951b35","tid":1538593,"uid":190078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:23:42.000Z","msg":"仲４大？　抗爭最忌同時多要求，目標不夠清晰，因為<br />\n１）要求太多<br />\n２）支持者難一致認同<br />\n３）對家易避重就輕地回應及攻擊我地既訴求<br />\n４）要求多但又缺一不可，對家就借機會唔妥協，運動膠著<br />\n５）有偏頗性，追求公義如我們，點可以又放示威者又追究警察，只能雙方同時拉／特赦<br />\n<br />\n所以本席宣佈，僅代表連登仔：一大訴求，雙真普選！！！"},{"pid":"a0df3d73c56fe228d5a31ef875c4d092a0e404e6","tid":1538593,"uid":134107,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kybLqX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkybLqX5.jpg&h=ae2d5f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n入嚟幫手推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"9e7a8ec61e8e2c1c0646c41c70b1c9418f74cf45","tid":1538593,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:24:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eaddeccb3a8408805f114e0dce75cf9f30bb416e","tid":1538593,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3be4e9f530bd8272ef9dd57bcbb917cf5944d9","tid":1538593,"uid":44870,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"行撚開啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"b61de64e0c7d55a6f9d44f6e300f78a34a495151","tid":1538593,"uid":169162,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:06.000Z","msg":"吓，義士唔係condom啊。。。"},{"pid":"5fe7adf0de310c421796bc4991f7711bdbe3ccad","tid":1538593,"uid":241904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:28:12.000Z","msg":"佢而家撤回根本係想我地8/9少人出黎,咁9/9美國復會就未必過到香港人權關係法<br />\n撤回係3個月前既訴求<br />\n而家係五大訴求,缺一不可<br />\n如果唔係只會每幾年就有一過revolution"},{"pid":"cbbba385df995cb3323a4b6d2fb3ddc3a04e4902","tid":1538593,"uid":190078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b61de64e0c7d55a6f9d44f6e300f78a34a495151","tid":1538593,"uid":169162,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:06.000Z","msg":"吓，義士唔係condom啊。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"有道理，應雙方同時特赦，或由首位真民選特首去決定（嚴重罪案如酷刑罪不能特赦，其餘沒有引致嚴重受傷的全特赦）"},{"pid":"1a1a81767205a6abc35b77161f77e30344f2155c","tid":1538593,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割？撤回都唔割！"},{"pid":"3fe2f0ec0d102b9cdec766b4185b3827a86e1aea","tid":1538593,"uid":38066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:30:02.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"d9c4162727bafa9a186892111d0a0ebcb12302b2","tid":1538593,"uid":157138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"你憑咩代表連登仔啊，呢到無人識你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052b14282b91628314e7c5aa43e32b5fde6ac668","tid":1538593,"uid":34088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:31:13.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 <br />\n缺一不可"},{"pi